.\" vim: tw=72 fdm=marker cms=.\\"\ %s
.
.\" FRONT MATTER {{{
.Dd Feb 04, 2016
.Os
.Dt REPOSE-ADD 1
.
.Sh NAME
.Nm repose\ add
.Nd Add matching repositories
.\" FRONT MATTER }}}
.
.\" SYNOPSIS {{{
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl h | \-help
.Nm
.Op Fl n | \-print
.Oo Fl t Ar TAG Oc Ns ...
.Ar HOST Ns ...
.Li --
.Ar REPA Ns ...
.\" SYNOPSIS }}}
.
.\" DESCRIPTION {{{
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
adds, in each
.Ar HOST ,
any number of package repositories.
.Nm
uses
.Xr repoq 1
to generate
.Nm zypper Cm addrepo
commands.
.\" }}}
.
.\" OPTIONS {{{
.Sh OPTIONS
.
.Bl -tag -width "xx"
. It Fl h
Display usage instructions.
. It Fl \-help
Display this manual page.
.
. It Fl n Ns , Fl \-print
Write destructive operations to standard output,
do not actually perform them.
.
. It Fl t Ns , Fl \-tag Ns Li = Ns Ar TAG
Override default
.Ar TAG Ns s
for tagless
.Ar REPA Ns s.
See
.Ar REPA
in
.Sx OPERANDS
below and
.Fl t , \-tag No in Xr repoq 1 .
.El
.\" }}}
.
.\" OPERANDS {{{
.Sh OPERANDS
.
.Bl -tag -width "xx"
. It Ar HOST
Machine to operate on
.Pq see Xr repose 1 .
. It Ar REPA
Repository pattern (see
. Xr repose 1 Ns )
with these extra requirements:
. Pp
. Bl -bullet -compact -offset "xx"
. It
. Sy P
cannot be empty
. It
. Sy V
can be empty, in which case version string of the
. Em baseproduct
is used
. It
. Sy A
can be empty, in which case architecture name of the
. Em baseproduct
is used
. It
. Sy T
defaults to
.Sy gm,lt,se,up .
. El
.El
.\" }}}
.
.\" EXAMPLES {{{
.Sh EXAMPLES
Add the
.Sy at Ns -
and
.Sy nv Ns -tagged
repositories for whatever
.Sy sled
version and architecture
.Sy fubar.example.org
is on.
.Bd -literal -offset "xxx"
$ repose add root@fubar.example.org -- sled:::at,nv
.Ed
.Pp
Add default-tagged repositories for
.Sy sle-sdk, sle-we
addons.
As in the previous example,
queries both hosts for their baseproduct versions and architectures.
.Bd -literal -offset "xxx"
$ repose add root@{fubar,snafu}.example.org -- sle-sdk sle-we
.Ed
.\" }}}
.
.\" SEE ALSO {{{
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr repoq 1 ,
.Xr repose-remove 1 ,
.Xr smrt 1 ,
.Xr ssh 1 ,
.Xr zypper 8 .
.\" }}}
.
.\" REPOSE {{{
.Sh REPOSE
.Nm
is part of
.Xr repose 1 .
.\" }}}
